<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>ANTILOCK BRAKES/TRACTION CONTROL: BENDIX - TROUBLESHOOTING - 2000, 4000 &#38; 8000 MODELS - TROUBLESHOOTING
        - INITIAL START-UP TEST PROCEDURE
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="IDcomponent" graphiccount="0">
        <title>INITIAL START-UP TEST PROCEDURE</title>
        <table id="t0403301" tblwidth="full-page" frame="all" numbered="no" view="reveal">
            <title>Initial Start-up Test Procedure</title>
            <tgroup cols="6" align="center" charoff="50" char="c">
                <colspec colnum="1" colname="1" colwidth="0.59in"/>
                <colspec colnum="2" colname="2" colwidth="0.60in"/>
                <colspec colnum="3" colname="3" colwidth="2.02in"/>
                <colspec colnum="4" colname="4" colwidth="0.75in"/>
                <colspec colnum="5" colname="5" colwidth="0.96in"/>
                <colspec colnum="6" colname="6" colwidth="1.73in" colsep="1"/>
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry colname="1">
                            <para>STEP</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="2">
                            <para>KEY</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="3">
                            <para>ACTION</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="4">
                            <para>SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="5">
                            <para>YES / IN SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry colname="6">
                            <para>NO / OUT OF SPEC.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody valign="top">
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>1.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Off</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Is vehicle equipped with Traction Control?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para></para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to Step 5.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>2.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Place the traction control panel switch to the ON position. Turn key ON and note if
                                the Traction Active light blinked ON, then turned OFF.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Light blinked ON then OFF?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to Step 5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>3.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Is the Traction Active light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Traction Active light ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_28.xml" xrefid="t0403322">TESTING TRACTION CONTROL SOLENOID
                                    ATR-1/ATR-2, PART B.
                                </hotlnk>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>4.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Is ABS dash light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ABS dash light ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_26.xml" xrefid="t0403320">TESTING TRACTION ACTIVE LIGHT
                                </hotlnk>
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_8.xml" xrefid="t0403302">ABS WARNING LIGHT DOES NOT TURN ON
                                </hotlnk>
                                .
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>5.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Is ABS dash light ON?</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ABS dash light ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_8.xml" xrefid="t0403302">ABS WARNING LIGHT DOES NOT TURN
                                    ON</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry>
                            <para>6.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Note if the ABS light blinked when it turned ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Light blinked.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to next step.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_9.xml" xrefid="t0403303">INSPECTING FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART
                                    A</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                    <row rowsep="1">
                        <entry>
                            <para>7.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>On</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ABS warning light flashes, then turns ON. Drive vehicle above 7 MPH for at least 5
                                seconds and note if ABS warning light stays ON.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>ABS light ON.</para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>Go to
                                <hotlnk document="s04033_10.xml" xrefid="t0403304">INSPECTION FOR ILLUMINATED LEDS, PART
                                    B</hotlnk>.
                            </para>
                        </entry>
                        <entry>
                            <para>The ABS system is functioning properly.</para>
                        </entry>
                    </row>
                </tbody>
            </tgroup>
        </table>
    </svcproc>
